{"tid":539949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：大家自己聽。浸會大學生的抗爭，就是這樣輸掉的。","createTime":"2018-01-25T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T10:51:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b6b26d449040ee5c445c3e1dafc20757050702","tid":539949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"大家沒有搞錯，你聽的正是大學生的發言、學生會會長的發言，不是語言教育中心的老師發言。如果你掩蓋了畫面，只是聽聲音，你會以為是語言中心教師抗議校方的發言。<br />\n香港學生提前進入官僚中產的身份，放棄了自己的抗爭主體。這是香港人鬥爭失敗的原因。幾年前，黃之鋒反對國民教育，用的理由也是國民教育諮詢不足夠，一副中產官僚的口吻，他根本不是反對國民教育，只是大家自作多情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BBCChinese/videos/10156104193183762/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBBCChinese%2Fvideos%2F10156104193183762%2F&d=7%2FhzJ5Rr0G53J4FA2T%2B399Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=f704386b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BBCChinese/videos/10156104193183762/</a>"},{"pid":"5c0e47237324c3a9dd01912487d82ce7a654e4dd","tid":539949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:47:46.000Z","msg":"若然語文中心一說他們將檢討評分標準，增加透明度，浸大生沒有理由拒絕普通話畢業試了。"},{"pid":"71347508dad6ce9ac05c9adeae6e783c25c19b9d","tid":539949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"陳雲：大學學生會會長，給你一個非常之pro（專業）的形象，他會專業地輸掉戰役，因為更好的報酬在後頭。"},{"pid":"1cfdd9e0faf3acc6ed8cff28510841d7d561328b","tid":539949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"評分準則...哈哈。<br />\n被人威脅，並唔係反檯，而係要求要點樣死法。<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8c13ae32541bbc9075437a71ce9b4fbee254f23c","tid":539949,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2016年唔出選新東就永遠唔會露底，哈哈"},{"pid":"66e3a0418b5286f1968bb14fcf8838caf598fe87","tid":539949,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"<